plot: Tensions escalate between Teresa, Louie, and the Fudas after a failed meeting. The Gorgas host a limoncello party. Danielle and Jennifer explore their conflict's root cause. Jackie campaigns against Margaret, who presents evidence.

Hostility remains at an all-time high between Teresa, Louie and the Fudas following their attempted sit down. Dolores discusses Paulie's recent job proposal with her mom and daughter. The Gorgas throw a limoncello-themed housewarming party where they receive an unwelcome gift. Danielle and Jennifer Aydin dig deeper into the root cause of their contention. Jackie continues to campaign against Margaret, who brings out the receipts.
